<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的新房子看上去真是太棒了！” 一个女人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她丈夫点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想快点儿进去看看。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21324</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个穿工作服，戴安全帽的大个子男人站在旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“进去吧！” 他说，“你们会喜欢的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>夫妻俩走了进去，女人大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有东西都是歪的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人挠了挠头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“建筑工人做得太差了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他转身要出去的时候，地板裂开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>夫妻俩尖叫着掉进了黑暗中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃，这几天一直下雨，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>好烦啊！” 玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70963</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们走在上学的路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天上堆满乌云，雨轻轻地下着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也是，” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“感觉好像已经下了几个星期了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想看到太阳。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我喜欢下雨。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86583</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克抬起头，张开嘴，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用舌头接住了几滴雨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔擦着眼镜上的雨水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也讨厌一整天都下雨，” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98110</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这就意味着......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“得在室内休息！” 玛拉抱怨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“室内休息很没劲。” 杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他踩了一下水坑，水花溅得到处都是。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太无聊了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雨下大了，朋友们走得更快了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大雨滴落在他们的雨伞上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“学校今天安静了，” 玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130547</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“施工终于结束了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130547</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过去的三个星期，学校里每天都有工人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘校长说，楼太旧了，需要修理。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔转头看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我希望火箭女孩儿今天什么也不用做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉看过来问：“为什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔耸耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“下雨呢！在雨里打坏人一定会很难。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克笑了。“怎么会呢！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火箭女孩儿超级厉害，一点儿雨算什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西飞快地看了特勒尔一眼，笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169124</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我同意特勒尔的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火箭女孩儿应该也不想打坏人的时候被淋湿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174463</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们到学校的时候，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180028</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她悄悄地离开朋友们，站在了大楼的旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长，” 她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>市长看上去很担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿， 我也不确定！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我给史密斯侦探打电话，但他一直不接，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203159</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>别的警官也不接。我担心他们出事了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203160</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您别担心，市长，” 罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会查清楚的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>